		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Armor (Large Shield) - Very Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 1 Minute</p><p><strong>Utility</strong></p><ul><li><p>The Shield leaps into the air and hovers in your space to protect you as if you were wielding it, leaving your hands free.</p></li><li><p>The Shield remains animate until you take a Bonus Action to end this effect, or until you die or are &amp;Reference[Incapacitated apply=false], at which point the Shield falls to the ground or into your hand if you have one free.</p></li></ul>",
